    {
        "content": "<p>uweigand created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12523#discussion_r2768942737\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This is again unnecessary.</p>\n</blockquote>",
